title: Contributing family workers, female (% of female employment) (modeled ILO estimate)
name: sl.fam.work.fe.zs
readme: Contributing family workers are those workers who hold "self-employment jobs" as own-account workers in a market-oriented establishment operated by a related person living in the same household.
